@startuml
title Flow B: Draft Save → Schedule → Publish & Monitor

actor User
participant ORCH as "Orchestrator(API)"
participant DB as "DB"
participant SYNC as "Synchro"
participant SCH as "Scheduler"
participant ADPT as "Adapter"

User -> ORCH : Draft 저장(본문+메타데이터)
ORCH -> DB : insert Draft/Metadata
ORCH -> SYNC : ingest(Draft) [async enqueue]

User -> ORCH : 발행 일정 + 모니터링 세그먼트 설정
ORCH -> SCH : createSchedule(post_id, segments, horizon caps)
SCH --> ORCH : schedule_id

== Publish at scheduled time ==
SCH -> ADPT : publish(account, post_payload, schedule_at)
ADPT --> SCH : {platform_post_id, posted_at, external_url}
SCH -> DB : update Post→posted, save link

== Monitoring segment(s) ==
loop for each segment window
  SCH -> ADPT : fetch_metrics(platform_post_id, window)
  ADPT --> SCH : {impressions, likes, comments,...}
  SCH -> SYNC : ingest(MonitoringResult) [async enqueue]
end

ORCH <-- User : 타임라인/진행률 조회
@enduml
